nodes.text: The Feenix system was a system in the Mid Rim. It contained the planet of Feenix. Han Solo, during a visit to this system, ended up bilking a Moff's assistant alongside Xaverri.
"Unstated Canon in Star Wars: The Essential Atlas" – Continuity, Criticisms, and Captain Panaka, Daniel Wallace's StarWars.com Blog (content now obsolete; archived from the original)
